// TODO(port): the following are cross-crate imports that will resolve in Phase B:
//   - LuaDebug  (lua_Debug struct; Phase E debug)
//   - HookEvent (LUA_HOOKCALL / LUA_HOOKLINE / LUA_HOOKCOUNT constants)
